            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>pak choi</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop the base off the <strong>pak choi</strong> and discard, then slice in half lengthways</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1620750212326-x200.jpg",
